name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Printable Chess Move List for Chess.com

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gives you a printable list of the moves in your game.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you've always wanted to print out your moves after a game, this is for you. Click one button and you get an easy to print move list.
Please note: come out of "focus mode" to print the move list.
